<head>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Hiragino Maru Gothic Pro', sans-serif;
    }

    .hero {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
      text-align: center;
      color: #000;
      background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7)), url('428625.jpg');
      background-position: left center; /* 左寄せ */
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-size: cover;
    }

    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      background-color: #007f5f;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 24px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }

    .cta-button:hover {
      background-color: #00593f;
    }

    .intro {
      margin-top: 40px;
      font-size: 20px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .intro p {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="hero">
    <a href="#" class="cta-button">問診を始める</a>
    <div class="intro">
      <p>身体の痛みをケアしましょう</p>
      <p>自宅でできるセルフケア方法を学びましょう</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
